| Project | Structure | CSS framework | Vite/Tauri dev port | Whisper | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **reaper** | Cargo **workspace** (`apps/<app>-gui/src-tauri`, `core/*`, `lib/*`) | **Vanilla CSS only** | **5173** | yes (`lib/whisper-common`) | yt-dlp/ffmpeg music archiver. Reference for layout + release. |
| **textmerger** | **Single crate** (`textmerger/src-tauri`) | Vanilla CSS (some legacy Tailwind ΓÇö do **not** add new Tailwind) | **5174** | no | Reference for the simple single-crate setup. |
| **vesta** | Cargo **workspace** (`apps/srt-gui/src-tauri`, `core/*`, `lib/*`, `cli/*`) | **Tailwind CSS v4** (`@import "tailwindcss";`) | **5175** | yes (`lib/whisper-common`) | Subtitles/Whisper/flashcards. Reference for Whisper + i18n tooling. |
